@page "/story"

<PageTitle>Our Story</PageTitle>

<section class="page-intro story-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
    <h1>Built for the quiet exchange between craft and care.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
        Artisanal Brew began as a shared table: one founder pulling espresso, another baking before sunrise, both interested in
        the kind of hospitality that makes time feel wider.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="story-image story-image--wide"></section>

<section class="story-block story-block--asymmetric">
    <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Founders</p>
        <h2>A room shaped by ritual.</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        Every detail is tuned for slower attention: marble counters that hold morning light, ceramics with weight, and a menu
        that changes only when the ingredients ask it to.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="story-split">
    <div class="story-image story-image--portrait"></div>
    <div class="story-panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Philosophy</p>
        <h2>Nothing rushed, nothing crowded.</h2>
        <p>
            We source coffee for clarity and sweetness, bake in small batches, and leave room between tables so conversation can
            settle naturally.
        </p>
        <a class="button button--ghost" href="visit">Plan a visit</a>
    </div>
</section>
